{"tid":1308262,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"火星疑發現有生物存在，NASA 好奇號影到有雀仔飛過！","createTime":"2019-07-12T00:25:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T00:39:34.000Z","uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c7277ebe6450bc89008253382757c65239554388","tid":1308262,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T00:25:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.express.co.uk/news/weird/1149820/nasa-alien-proof-nasa-curiosity-mars-rover-photo-flying-bird-ufo-mars-conspiracy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.express.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fweird%2F1149820%2Fnasa-alien-proof-nasa-curiosity-mars-rover-photo-flying-bird-ufo-mars-conspiracy&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0A5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=61a67e33\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.express.co.uk/news/weird/1149820/nasa-alien-proof-nasa-curiosity-mars-rover-photo-flying-bird-ufo-mars-conspiracy</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/hottopic/20190711001608-260809\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Fhottopic%2F20190711001608-260809&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0A5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=cb5c9e80\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/hottopic/20190711001608-260809</a><br />\n<br />\n宇宙中是否還有其他生物，一直是人類研究的目標，美國國家航空暨太空總署也派出好奇號（Curiosity），探測火星氣候及地質，希望能發現生物。日前一名業餘UFO觀察家在研究NASA拍的照片時，發現火星天空上竟出現一個詭異黑點，模樣像是一隻飛翔的鳥，讓專家們直呼不可思議。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hqrcgbm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHqrcgbm.png&h=36a61c13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據《express》報導，幽浮專家華林（Scott C Waring）日前在部落格寫下「這驚人一幕是伊拉佐斯塔(Marcelo Irazusta)發現的，火星上空好像有一隻鳥飛過，上週被好奇號(Curiosity Rover)拍下」，而這張驚人照片為編號SOL 2446，華林認為這可能是一艘飛碟，但也提出質疑「它看起來很像一隻飛上空的老鷹」。"},{"pid":"1d1928fd3b324ef405a920b4090f9cff4f7b04b4","tid":1308262,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T00:26:19.000Z","msg":"華林認為，假若此照為真，其一就是火星上真的有生物，要不然就是這張照並非於火星拍攝，而是在地球上一個與火星相似的地方，例如加拿大的德文島(Devon Island），「德文島是一座荒涼的無人島嶼，美國宇航局已多次前往，在地球上類似火星的環境中測試火星檢測車」，因此又被科學家稱為「地球上的火星」。<br />\n<br />\n不過也有人指出，這個黑點可以確定並非鏡頭污漬，但有可能是宇宙線(又稱為宇宙射線)，或是由太陽光反射造成，而宇宙射線是太空中帶電高能次原子粒子，佈滿於宇宙間，由於地球有大氣層保護，因此才免於遭宇宙射線轟擊，而火星上的大氣層稀薄，因此對於宇宙輻射並沒有防護力。"},{"pid":"130b5ed2019556fa9d51e6c4bd5d473a865ff8fa","tid":1308262,"uid":10125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T00:28:23.000Z","msg":"黑點呢？"},{"pid":"b55ae58078cca1ce79ac071c8ddc3fbc781c3d81","tid":1308262,"uid":197540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T00:30:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可能有都唔定，雖然機會微<br />\n<br />\n火星凍地球少少，有大氣層<br />\n探測到有冰"},{"pid":"c7e26cc4f88edde72cb0eda20534ae61d94c3375","tid":1308262,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"130b5ed2019556fa9d51e6c4bd5d473a865ff8fa","tid":1308262,"uid":10125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T00:28:23.000Z","msg":"黑點呢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T00:37:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn5.newsnation.in/images/2019/07/07/nasafinding-1000_8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn5.newsnation.in%2Fimages%2F2019%2F07%2F07%2Fnasafinding-1000_8.jpg&h=6c1dd6cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newsnation.in/science-news/did-nasa-photograph-a-flying-bird-on-mars-details-inside-article-229913.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsnation.in%2Fscience-news%2Fdid-nasa-photograph-a-flying-bird-on-mars-details-inside-article-229913.html&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0A5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=aa764035\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.newsnation.in/science-news/did-nasa-photograph-a-flying-bird-on-mars-details-inside-article-229913.html</a>"},{"pid":"791173a7cef9378f2de2e19e9bcff39d5ea8ef1d","tid":1308262,"uid":209248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T00:39:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}